《'''天幕杀机'''》（{{lang-en|''Skyfall''}}）， 是2012年上映的第23部[[詹姆斯·邦德|詹姆斯·邦德]]电影《[[007：大破天幕杀机|007：大破天幕杀机]]》的同名主题曲，由英国女歌手[[愛黛兒|愛黛兒]]演唱<ref name="Adele theme">"[http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/19785659 Adele confirms Skyfall Bond theme song] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20121204163556/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/19785659 |date=2012-12-04 }}" BBC Newsbeat, retrieved 1 October 2012</ref>, 詞曲由愛黛兒與制作人[[保羅·埃普沃思|保羅·埃普沃思]]完成，[[J·A·C·雷德福德|J·A·C·雷德福德]]負責[[編配|編配]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/OfficialAdele/status/252762323884847104/photo/1|title=Skyfall sheet|publisher=Adele Official [[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-10-01|accessdate=2012-10-01|archive-date=2012-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002230158/http://twitter.com/OfficialAdele/status/252762323884847104/photo/1|dead-url=no}}</ref> 作為纪念首部[[詹姆斯·邦德|詹姆斯·邦德]]电影《[[諾博士|諾博士]]》上映50周年的“世界詹姆斯·邦德日”活動的一部分，它於[[英國夏令時|英國夏令時]]10月5日0:07發布。<ref name=press>{{cite web|url=http://www.007.com/skyfall-official-theme-song-news/|title=Skyfall Official Theme Song News: Release To Coincide With Bond's 50th Anniverary|work=007.com|publisher=[[Eon_Productions|Eon Productions]]|date=2012-10-01|accessdate=2012-10-01|archive-date=2013-01-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DxHNzaD5?url=http://www.007.com/skyfall-official-theme-song-news/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

《天幕杀机》在2013年1月的[[第70届金球奖|第70届金球奖]]仪式上赢得了[[金球奖最佳歌曲|金球奖最佳歌曲]]。随后，它在2013年[[全英音乐奖|全英音乐奖]]上获得了最佳英国单曲。在[[第85届奥斯卡颁奖典礼|第85届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]上，这首歌成为了自1982年的《{{link-en|For Your Eyes Only|For Your Eyes Only (song)}}》以来首获提名和历史上首次获得[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲|奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲]]的[[詹姆斯·邦德|詹姆斯·邦德]]电影主题曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2013/01/10/oscar-nominations-2013-adele-skyfall_n_2446722.html|title=Oscar Nominations 2013: Adele's 'Skyfall', 'Les Miserables' And Daniel Day-Lewis Lead British Hopes|publisher=The Huffington Post|date=2013-01-10|accessdate=2013-01-10|archive-date=2013-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130113071104/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2013/01/10/oscar-nominations-2013-adele-skyfall_n_2446722.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/oscars/9793191/Oscars-2013-Adele-nomination-saves-total-Skyfall-snub.html|title=Oscars 2013: Adele nomination saves total Skyfall snub|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2013-01-10|accessdate=2013-01-10|archive-date=2013-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130112014512/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/oscars/9793191/Oscars-2013-Adele-nomination-saves-total-Skyfall-snub.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿黛尔到场领奖并首次现场演唱这首歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.007.com/skyfall-official-theme-song-news/|title=Skyfall Official Theme Song News: Release To Coincide With Bond's 50th Anniverary|publisher=[[Eon_Productions|Eon Productions]]|date=2012-10-01|accessdate=2012-10-01|archive-date=2013-01-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DxHNzaD5?url=http://www.007.com/skyfall-official-theme-song-news/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

